Package: smtp-sink
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Minimal SMTP sink for local development and testing
 smtp-sink receives emails via SMTP and exposes them via HTTP for
 inspection. Features include:
  - SMTP server with AUTH (PLAIN/LOGIN) support
  - STARTTLS and implicit TLS
  - HTTP REST API and WebSocket for real-time updates
  - Web UI for visual inspection
  - Catch-all routing for any recipient domain
